                    <p><strong>Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong></p>
                    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Significant changes will be communicated via our website, and the effective date at the top of this document will be updated.<br><br>

                    <p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p>
                    If you have any questions or concerns regarding our Privacy Policy, please reach out to us:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Email: </strong>Will@edwardscapes.com</li>
                        <li><strong>Phone: </strong>(434) 942-2455</li>
                        <li><strong>Address: </strong>P.O. Box 10171 Lynchburg, VA 24506</li>
